{"tid":1534801,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生投訴教學","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:28:32.000Z","uid":38075,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5d4a246f81ba1d6cce6cacc08df376a7195f49","tid":1534801,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"各位中學生可以細閱，點樣可以反抗到學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學校投訴教學：<br />\n<br />\n1. 搜料：學校九成老師都唔熟法律，所以學生一定要詳細紀錄學校打壓罷課既行動，最好記低埋時間﹑錄埋音。如果寫過任何口供紙/違規紀錄既，一定要攞一份留底。唔好比學校加鹽加醋。<br />\n<br />\n2. 揾位入：搜到料後，其實你可以慢慢揾下有咩可以入佢。坦白講，現行法例好保障學生的。例如如果有學校禁錮學生罰企，其實可以告體罰(法律上只可罰學生企15分鐘)；又如有老師出言恐嚇而令學生心靈受創既，一樣可以告。甚至老師拍打一下學生既，已經可以告普通襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n3. 正式立案：一定要先揾校監/家長教師會/家長校董，一定要嘈上校董會，仲要揾埋教育局同區議員介入。有教局同區議員，學校就唔敢耍太極。<br />\n<br />\n4. 分頭行事：老師咁忙，又受投訴壓力，教學表現一定下降，呢個時候，可以揾其他家長，儲齊佢批改過既功課，睇下有冇咩錯漏，如有，再就「專業失當」揾教局同校董開多個投訴。基本上，中文科既，作文睇少幾個錯別字；理科睇唔到串錯字，已經可以立案投訴。呢樣投訴分分鐘搞到個老師精神病都得。<br />\n<br />\n4. 一定要佢比明確限期回覆，一定要確實日期，同埋要校方交代清楚係邊個處理。如果有問題揾邊個？到時邊個覆？點樣覆，全部白紙黑字要佢簽名作實。如果佢開既期限太長，問清楚原因。然後定時打電話問佢追查既進度。"},{"pid":"1c6d65f99528d8cf1227af3d3e19045b2f5d6e39","tid":1534801,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:24:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f33242b08095f0752696609409d4cae1a0f7375","tid":1534801,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:28:31.000Z","msg":"一齊杯葛個老師<br />\n佢教書寫黑板就掟柒佢"},{"pid":"9f330d8946474667a22e69b96e728cc11537e721","tid":1534801,"uid":292881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:28:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2edeadb4ef182de7f797e10ccfca8229a98ee9b","tid":1534801,"uid":167808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:30:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e80106aee580f2472db199e6d0f11ee4c6bd26e","tid":1534801,"uid":108415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:20:36.000Z","msg":"學校最怕聲譽跌 <br />\n只要推到有人知就得 <br />\n班教畜仲驚過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8QXuKJa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8QXuKJa.png&h=e0150f18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6250e6ed3b6852fc60a73c9eebd0ddc127265fc","tid":1534801,"uid":250164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:31:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0f52da09d65dcb639aafe6f3b5806f774e7d7bf","tid":1534801,"uid":200718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd11402719e59ea320b265c4a005a7c99d8891ad","tid":1534801,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>未爛未拆 咁樣入！</strong></span></span><br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/w